Cell.Data: There is no door in your house
You can sleep and store your gear in your houseb (WIP). To switch into CONSTRUCTION MODE, click on the button below.
你可以在房子中休息和存放你的战利品(开发中）。 点击下面的按钮切换到建造模式。
When placing a new tile of GROUND, a selectionned WALL will be automatically linked to it if there is none. You can also change each WALL by going in the WALL TAB.
当你在地上放置一块新的瓷砖时，当前商店中选中的墙会自动与之链接。 你也可以选择墙选项卡来改变每一面墙的样式。

You can place any furniture you like! To ROTATE an object, maintain the RIGHT CLICK, or use the keys [Q] and [D]. You can also choose the size of the GRID and SNAP furnitures for a more precise placing.
你可以放置任何你喜欢的家具！ 要旋转物体，请按住滚轮不放，或使用键[Q]和[D]。 你还可以选择网格和吸附的精度以便更精确的控制布局。

Every object you place is displayed in the LIST. Once you want to buy the assets, just click on CONFIRM, and they'll be your. Removed object that are paid are stocked for future use. At the moment, only Gold is needed to pay, but a crafting notion will be added in the game.
你放置的每个物体都显示在右侧的列表中。 假如你想购买材料，只需选中并确认，就可以购买。已购买但被移除的物体会收入仓库以备将来使用。 目前只需用金币支付，未来会加入更多建筑材料。
